'''阿赫馬杜·巴巴托拉·阿希喬'''（{{Lang-en|'''Ahmadou Babatoura Ahidjo'''}}，1924年8月24日－1989年11月30日<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://face2faceafrica.com/article/the-story-of-cameroons-first-president-who-unified-its-french-and-english-regions-in-1961|title=The story of Cameroon's first president who unified its French and English regions in 1961|date=30 October 2018|website=Face2Face Africa|language=en|access-date=25 September 2019|archive-date=2022-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220211233645/https://face2faceafrica.com/article/the-story-of-cameroons-first-president-who-unified-its-french-and-english-regions-in-1961|dead-url=no}}</ref>）[[喀麥隆|喀麥隆]]獨裁者，是第一任[[喀麥隆總統|喀麥隆總統]]，其任期從1960至1982年，當權長達22年。

